cics_dfhccutl – Initialize CICS local catalog¶

  • Synopsis

  • Parameters

  • Examples

  • Return Values

Synopsis¶

  • Initialize the CICS local catalog by invoking the DFHCCUTL program.

Parameters¶

dfhlcd

Specify the input local catalog data set

required: True
type: str
steplib

Specify a partioned data set containing DFHCCUTL.

required: True
type: str

Examples¶

- name: Initialize the LCD
  cics_local_catalog_initialization:
    steplib: CTS550.CICS720.SDFHLOAD
    dfhlcd: BJMAXY.CICS.IYK3ZMX7.DFHLCD

Return Values¶

msg
The execution result message.
returned: always
type: str
sample: The DFHCCUTL program executed successfully.
rc
The return code.
returned: always
type: str
content
The output data set for results, information and error/dump messages.
returned: always
type: str
changed
Indicates if any changes were made during module operation.
returned: always
type: bool
